{"tid":1059190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍天晴邨男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-03-13T03:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T03:49:46.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"83d4773f0d77a2d5fe0dc5fc4572ffe799ab050b","tid":1059190,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/photo/bkn-20190313092922808-0313_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190313105055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190313%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190313092922808-0313_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190313105055&h=832454db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女親友到場助查。（張世洋攝）<br />\n天水圍發生墮樓案，今早(13日)5時07分，一名年約60歲男子被發現由高處墮下，倒臥在天晴邨晴海樓平台，奄奄一息，救護員接報到場，證實男子已氣絕身亡。警方調查後，聯絡上死者的一名女親友到場助查，正了解其墮樓原因 。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/mobile/bkn-20190313092922808-0313_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190313%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190313092922808-0313_00822_001.html&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=b783464a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/mobile/bkn-20190313092922808-0313_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b7f2c8565471f83fe6a5c1188d66892e664739a2","tid":1059190,"uid":10692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fa7da4e0be384770d4f9e61ce4611282ff2086e","tid":1059190,"uid":92859,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"廢老-1"}]}